title: 10 Fantastic Instagram Filters for Fall 2020
description: The weather's changing and fall fashion is in style. Up your social media game with these fantastic fall-themed filters for Instagram.
intro: The weather's changing and fall fashion is in style. Whether you are looking to add a nice fall vibe to your photos and videos, or you are looking for something a little more goofy, we have you covered with 10 fantastic Instagram filters to celebrate autumn.

filters.name: fallen leaves
filters.author: ChloeÌ
filters.description: It's that time of year when the leaves start falling. Bring the magic of autumn into your own home without the hassle of needing to rake up leaves.

filters.name: pumpkin
filters.author: denisoovas
filters.description: We might be done carving jack-o-lanterns, but pumpkins are still very much a part of fall. This filter will help you blend in with the rest of the fall decorations so you can hide from your crazy aunt or uncle. You know the one.

filters.name: Pumpkin Spice Bae
filters.author: Isabelle Udo
filters.description: This is a super cool filter that will turn your head into an autumn forest. It's super creative and captures that autumn feeling while still being delightfully different and unique.

filters.name: Autumn Wreath
filters.author: Fishdom
filters.description: Wreaths aren't just for Christmas! Celebrate the falltime with this festive autumn wreath upon your head.

filters.name: pumpkin spice
filters.author: brittany
filters.description: Capture that vintage fall vibe with this excellent filter from Brittany. The grain and the faded colors make it feel nice and cozy.

filters.name: TurkeyHead
filters.author: VRCraftworks
filters.description: It might start off with sort of a Christmas feel, but this one still works for the fall. I mean, who doesn't want to turn themselves into a roast turkey?

filters.name: The Corny Filter
filters.author: Anon A. Mister
filters.description: This might be the wackiest filter on the list, but it's a good one. It's harvest time, so enjoy being an ear of corn while you can.

filters.description: This simple filter adds a warm, orange hue to everything. Perfect for making those fall colors pop. It works best on scenes with wood and those red and orange and yellow hues.

filters.name: FALL
filters.author: Ayo Vega
filters.description: This is a really neat filter that adds a nice fall bouquet on your head. It looks a little plain at first, but smile and bright red flowers start to bloom!

filters.name: FALL PRESET
filters.author: Sameer Mahan
filters.description: And let's finish off our list with a warm yet subdued color filter. Similar to the other color filters on our list, this filter adds a warm orange hue to everything.
